description: The redevelopment of Seager Buildings Site, Deptford Bridge/Brookmill Road and the Norfolk House Site, Brookmill Road SE8, to provide a ground plus 26-storey residential tower, a part 5/part 6 storey building fronting Brookmill Road, a 5 storey stepped building rising to 11 storeys, a 3 storey courtyard building, two storey roof extension on Holland House fronting Deptford Bridge and the retention of International House, comprising 207 private residential units, 96 affordable homes, 7 live/work units and a total of 4,697 m² of commercial floorspace, including a café/restaurant, gymnasium, retail unit and art gallery, together with 60 basement car parking spaces, associated motor bike/scooter and 393 bicycle spaces and landscaping.
site_name: SITE OF SEAGER BUILDINGS & NORFOLK HOUSE
